#. type: item
#: original_texis/files.texi:411
#, no-wrap
msgid "."
msgstr ""

#. type: table
#: original_texis/files.texi:414
msgid ""
"Save this buffer, then exit @code{save-some-buffers} without even asking "
"about other buffers."
